```

2. **GitHub Actions staging workflow：** 检查 name 或 content 中包含 "staging" 的 workflow files：
```bash
for f in $(find .github/workflows -maxdepth 1 \( -name '*.yml' -o -name '*.yaml' \) 2>/dev/null); do
